  "title": "M&E Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist Project Manager in supervising and coordinating all services and complete within programme</li>\n  <li>Manage M&amp;E subcontractors to execute mechanical and electrical works in construction</li>\n  <li>Supervise M&amp;E subcontractor day to day site works</li>\n  <li>Conduct in detailed, M&amp;E coordination with all specialist contractors</li>\n  <li>Carry out testing and commission of M&amp;E work</li>\n  <li>Ensure contractor comply with all necessary standards, code of practice and safety regulations</li>\n  <li>Any other adhoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma / Degree in Mechanical &amp; Electrical Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>3-5 years of relevant experience in supervision of M&amp;E works installation</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently</li>\n  <li>Good safety knowledge and attitude</li>\n</ul>",
